* Prioritize *                 -*-muse-*-
Getting what you desire most

Most people don't really know what they want.  Consequently, they
don't get it.  The saying is, "He who aims at nothing hits it".  But
with a little reflection you can build the life you most want.

Life can be complex.  But if you know the art of priority then your
life becomes simpler.  There are a lot of things that just do not
matter.

You will get tips and ideas that will make you more effective in your
personal and work life.  Reduce your stress and have more fun.  Life is
too short to be ineffective at what you do.

Each article is fairly short and can be read quickly allowing you to
get one bite-sized nugget of wisdom at a time.  

As a Shrinking World Guide this content is free for you to use in any
way you wish.  Please give credit if you appreciate this material.

